Package: RRotF
Type: Package
Title: Random Rotation Forests
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Arnu Pretorius
Maintainer: Arnu Pretorius <arnupretorius@gmail.comt>
Description: Fits a rotation forest as proposed by Rodriguez et al. (2006)
    with randomised trees using orthogonal or oblique splits as base learners.
    The package is restricted to binary classification. (Code largely based on
    `RotationForest` package.)
License: MIT
LazyData: TRUE
Import: caret,
    randomForest,
    rpart,
    obliqueRF
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
